TITLE: Implementing Block Scoping in JavaScript vs ReScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how block scoping and implicit returns work differently between JavaScript and ReScript. JavaScript requires an IIFE while ReScript has natural block scope returns.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rescript-lang/rescript-lang.org.git/blob/master/pages/docs/manual/v10.0.0/overview.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_0

