TITLE: Implementing Async/Await in ReScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use async/await in ReScript. The code defines an async function that awaits the result of another async function and returns a greeting string.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rescript-lang/rescript-lang.org.git/blob/master/pages/docs/manual/v12.0.0/function.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_18

LANGUAGE: res
CODE:
