TITLE: Creating and Using Promises in ReScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a promise using Js.Promise.make and chain multiple promise operations using then_ and catch. It showcases the usage of the pipe operator for improved readability.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rescript-lang/rescript-lang.org.git/blob/master/pages/docs/manual/v9.0.0/promise.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: ReScript
