TITLE: Testing MutableSet Emptiness Example in ReasonML
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating how to check if a MutableSet is empty using the isEmpty function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rescript-lang/rescript-lang.org.git/blob/master/pages/docs/manual/v8.0.0/api/belt/mutable-set.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: reasonml
CODE:
```
module IntCmp =
  Belt.Id.MakeComparable({
    type t = int;
    let cmp = Pervasives.compare;
  });

let empty = Belt.MutableSet.fromArray([||], ~id=(module IntCmp));
let notEmpty = Belt.MutableSet.fromArray([|1|],~id=(module IntCmp));

Belt.MutableSet.isEmpty(empty); /* true */
Belt.MutableSet.isEmpty(notEmpty); /* false */
```

